<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='272877' id='t-272877'>Tom Rielly: So Max, by taking all these samples of,</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:47
