<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='276452' id='t-276452'>let's say, 10,000 people,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='279228' id='t-279228'>you'll be able to tell who's healthy and who's not?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='282082' id='t-282082'>What are you going to get out of those samples?</span>
</span>
</p>
